For information regarding COVID-19 Tests,  please visit:  COVID-19 Testing in Erie County

Village of Depew cases are counted half with the Cheektowaga total, and half with the Lancaster total.

The data in this application is provided by the Erie County Department of Health.  This website and its contents herein, including all data, mapping, and analysis is provided to the public strictly for educational and academic research purposes. 

For COVID-19 counts outside of Erie County, visit the Johns Hopkins Global COVID-19 map.
